      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from coupon-level tensile testing of production-lot Ti-6Al-4V; UHMWPE surrogate properties from supplier datasheet with lot verification.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus for the pedicle screw and rod were characterized from five tensile coupons machined from the same production lot used in bench testing. UHMWPE vertebral body surrogate properties were taken from the supplier datasheet and verified against three compression tests. Input uncertainty distributions were propagated through the Monte Carlo UQ campaign."
    },
