      "rationale": "The validation activity precisely replicates the COU: same device design, same test standard (ASTM F1717), same loading mode (compression-bending), and same acceptance thresholds used in the regulatory submission. No extrapolation in loading regime, geometry, or material is required to apply the validated model to the submission COU. Relevance is assessed as fully satisfactory."
